{"title":"Hexo & Inside","date":"2022-10-16T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 17, 2022","L":"10/17/2022","MM-DD":"10-17"},"link":"2022/10/17/blog/hexo-&-inside","tags":["Hexo","blog","github","theme"],"categories":["blog"],"updated":"2022-10-18T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"pre-requirement\">pre-requirement<a title=\"#pre-requirement\" href=\"#pre-requirement\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>node.js &gt;= 8.10, recommand &gt;=10.0</li>\n<li>npm</li>\n<li>git</li>\n</ul>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"setup\">setup<a title=\"#setup\" href=\"#setup\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"install-theme---inside\">install theme - <code>Inside</code><a title=\"#install-theme---inside\" href=\"#install-theme---inside\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm i hexo-theme-inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"quick-qtart\">quick qtart<a title=\"#quick-qtart\" href=\"#quick-qtart\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"modify-the-global-_config.yml\">modify the global <code>_config.yml</code><a title=\"#modify-the-global-_config.yml\" href=\"#modify-the-global-_config.yml\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><figcaption><span>_config.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">inside</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"theme-configuration\">theme configuration<a title=\"#theme-configuration\" href=\"#theme-configuration\"></a></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>create a config file named <code>_config.inside.yml</code></li>\n<li>Copy <a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/_config.yml\" target=\"_blank\">theme config yml</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"setup-for-github-action\">setup for github action<a title=\"#setup-for-github-action\" href=\"#setup-for-github-action\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>create a new repo named ‘<code>username</code>.github.io’ where username is your account name of github</li>\n<li>install dependency <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm i hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>modify the section <code>deploy</code> inside <code>_config.yml</code>, be sure to modify the <code>username</code><br>\nfor more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/github-pages.html#%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88%E9%A0%81%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/github-pages.html#專案頁面</a></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><figcaption><span>_config.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">type:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;git&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">repo:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;https://github.com/username/username.github.io&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;main&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"usage\">usage<a title=\"#usage\" href=\"#usage\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"create-a-new-post\">create a new post<a title=\"#create-a-new-post\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\">Writing</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"run-server\">run server<a title=\"#run-server\" href=\"#run-server\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\">Server</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"generate-static-files\">generate static files<a title=\"#generate-static-files\" href=\"#generate-static-files\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\">Generating</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"clean-the-workspace\">clean the workspace<a title=\"#clean-the-workspace\" href=\"#clean-the-workspace\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo cl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites,-ex.-github\">deploy to remote sites, ex. github<a title=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites,-ex.-github\" href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites,-ex.-github\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\">Deployment</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"generate-&amp;-deploy\">generate &amp; deploy<a title=\"#generate-&amp;-deploy\" href=\"#generate-&amp;-deploy\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hedo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"Split Horizon (Distance Vector)","link":"2022/10/18/networking/split-horizon"},"next":{"title":"OSPF NSF Introduction","link":"2022/10/17/networking/ospf-nsf"},"plink":"https://jason19970210.github.io/2022/10/17/blog/hexo-&-inside/","toc":[{"id":"pre-requirement","title":"pre-requirement","index":"1"},{"id":"setup","title":"setup","index":"2"},{"id":"install-theme---inside","title":"install theme - Inside","index":"3"},{"id":"quick-qtart","title":"quick qtart","index":"4"},{"id":"setup-for-github-action","title":"setup for github action","index":"5"},{"id":"usage","title":"usage","index":"6"}],"reading_time":"252 words in 2 min"}